sentences: Robin Daniel Skinner (born 15 December 1998), known professionally as Cavetown (sometimes stylized in all lowercase), is an English singer-songwriter, record producer and YouTuber.
His YouTube channel, which he began in November 2012, sits at 1.79 million subscribers and 321 million video views as of December 2021.
Skinner released his fourth studio album, Sleepyhead, in March 2020.
Skinner was born in Oxford, England on 15 December 1998.
He was raised in Cambridge and attended Parkside Community College from 2010 to 2015 and Hills Road Sixth Form College until 2017.
